Don Alden STACKS v. UNITED STATES of America. No. 5516. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Jan. 4, 1957.

No appearance for appellant.

Paul W. Cress, U. S. Atty., and H. Dale Cook, Asst. U. S. Atty., Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellee.
